            <thetext>Fixed: I used a script that runs both optipng and pngcrush on each file and keeps the smaller file on the framework images. Looking at some files revealed that the optimized versions look far more blurry when scaled up significantly (&gt; 200%). Since we use scaled images in some of the decorators, we decided to only optimize the &quot;icon&quot; subfolder for now.</thetext>
